a(id="mixins" href="#mixins")
  h2 mixins

p all html is lowercase, anything starting with an uppercase letter is a
  | mixin. Arguments and parens are optional.

  pre.input
    code.
      Person(firstName, lastName)
        h1= firstName
        h2= lastName

p use mixins by putting a `+` before the name of the mixin. Arguments and
  | parens are optional.

  pre.input
    code.
      +Person('Jello', 'Biafra')
